## PLACEHOLDERS

- `<PROJECT_NAME>`: Your project name
- `<SEGREGATED_ACCOUNT>`: GitHub account for dev workstation
- `<PERSONAL_ACCOUNT>`: Personal GitHub account (forbidden on dev machine)
- `<GIT_USER>` / `<GIT_EMAIL>`: Git identity for dev workstation
- `<VAULT_ACCOUNT>` / `<VAULT_SERVER>`: Password vault details
- `<SSH_KEY_PATH>`: Path to SSH key file
- `<FIDO_APP_NAME>`: FIDO2 application label (e.g., `ssh:my-account`)
- `<SK_PROVIDER_PATH>`: Path to sk-libfido2.dylib or equivalent
- `<KEY_FILENAME>` / `<KEY_COMMENT>`: SSH key naming